=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度76%，基於211條評論，平均分為6.59/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_good_dinosaur/ |title=The Good Dinosaur reviews |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621191555/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_good_dinosaur/ |archive-date=2016-06-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到66分<ref name="meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-good-dinosaur |title=The Good Dinosaur reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2015-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128041000/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-good-dinosaur |archive-date=2015-11-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分6.8，獲得普遍好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]表示：「恐龍當家提供了有價值的故事，即使它並不完全辜負[[皮克斯|皮克斯]]訂定的崇高標準，表現出了驚險漂亮的[[動畫|動畫]]，還增加了迷人的家庭友好的[[娛樂|娛樂]]。」據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/thanksgiving-box-office-hunger-games-mockingjay-creed-the-good-dinosaur-1201639941/|title=Katniss Rules Wednesday On Track For $78M-80M 5-Day; ‘Good Dinosaur’ Eyes $58M-$62M; ‘Creed’ Punching $39M-$42M|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|accessdate=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126233231/http://deadline.com/2015/11/thanksgiving-box-office-hunger-games-mockingjay-creed-the-good-dinosaur-1201639941/|archive-date=2015-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

